---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
List visible friends of the active account or another personal profile

Usage: list [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --user <USERNAME>
          Exact username whose visible friends should be listed

      --limit <N>
          Server request page size (maximum 50)

          [default: 10]

      --offset <N>
          Zero-based friend-list offset

          [default: 0]

  -h, --help
          Print help
